{"tid":2492572,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"主子初步確診FIV 想醫好佢","createTime":"2021-04-17T08:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T08:16:49.000Z","uid":251250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"97cf5978e845298f845437f5e55d80619967f982","tid":2492572,"uid":251250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:13:57.000Z","msg":"布偶貓 6個月大 <br />\n今日帶咗佢去愛協睇 獸醫話初步確診FIV <br />\n佢建議住院做手術去除肺積水 咁就即刻安排咗佢入院<br />\n睇醫生連住院費比咗九千幾 <br />\n<br />\n我仲係大學生 早排仲因運動同屋企人關係唔好<br />\n搬走咗屋企 喺深水埗租屋住 <br />\n本來租屋嘅錢 生活費 學費 已經月月清 <br />\n全部靠自己.... 點知貓貓就發生啲咁嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n平時貓貓係我返到屋企嘅精神支柱..<br />\n知道咗確診真係唔知仲可以點.... 淨係識喊<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知道可以點樣幫助到貓貓 <br />\n我上網睇過好似有針可以打但係唔知係邊度可以搵到"},{"pid":"b84893a349abbf5df65eb0994de86b5d352cf186","tid":2492572,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:14:45.000Z","msg":"FIP?"},{"pid":"4c29ba8081966dfd2acbf35abc7ad50a4dd81022","tid":2492572,"uid":251250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b84893a349abbf5df65eb0994de86b5d352cf186","tid":2492572,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:14:45.000Z","msg":"FIP?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:15:44.000Z","msg":"係啊FIP 啊 喊到打錯字都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf91054ce62f49bdda22d4355c09eef9b2a7876","tid":2492572,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"入fb group搵人賣針畀你打,<br />\n我隻貓都初步可能係fip, 今晚打第一針"}],"pinned":{"pid":"4c29ba8081966dfd2acbf35abc7ad50a4dd81022","tid":2492572,"uid":251250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:15:44.000Z","msg":"係啊FIP 啊 喊到打錯字都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}